{"tid":817654,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"ACER中伏？","createTime":"2018-09-13T13:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T09:37:34.000Z","uid":204923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"273375c93e7fb310b44a13df97a9e2a3334e40a3","tid":817654,"uid":204923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"我前2日買咗部新嘅switch 3一直冇事，幾個鐘前有個咩intel 儲存技術嘅嘢彈出嚟話建議backup個硬碟嘅資料，去到完成都冇事嘅。<br />\n睇咗陣片就放低咗部機去食飯<br />\n返到嚟就見佢黑曬屏鍵盤燈着曬冇反應，重新開機之後就彈no bootable device<br />\n上網search咗好耐試咗唔同嘅方法都唔得<br />\n最後見有人話重裝完佢就得咗我就去試<br />\n結果installation failed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心唔知仲可以點<br />\n<br />\n阿媽話拎去賣機嗰到問下先<br />\n但係其實我依家係咪只可以攞返去維修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3538e01f8d9b524ab7dc196b27641d35f5645f","tid":817654,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"Intel chips driver died?"},{"pid":"fc11866e64ee6621e4da09e051c43231324a3f52","tid":817654,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"好似唔關acer事wo"},{"pid":"6d256801219bc2126f207d58e0c7e2985aa75fde","tid":817654,"uid":204923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc11866e64ee6621e4da09e051c43231324a3f52","tid":817654,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"好似唔關acer事wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"所以咪加問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我完全唔知佢做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a27dffa10332bb20e80a071eed216d5cc7ce3c9","tid":817654,"uid":204923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f3538e01f8d9b524ab7dc196b27